  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK168">
<l>aḻukkā ṟeṉavoru pāvi tirucceṟṟut</l>
<l>tīyuḻi yuyttu viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Envy will destroy (a man's) wealth (in his world) and drive him into the pit of fire (in the world to come.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
